{"tid":976482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[玩屎]「看我真面目！」姊弟戀被拒噁男逼她甲賽","createTime":"2019-01-10T12:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T13:27:31.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f455e042151acdfa3bcebaff46cbbef2be64e8f9","tid":976482,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"新加坡1名28歲的堆高機駕駛A男，因為愛上大他21歲的女同事，屢屢求愛不成，竟將自己的糞便，塗到對方嘴上逼她「甲賽」，今天被法院判囚7天。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》報導，2017年5月A男與同事大姐相識，之後就展開追求，但A男屢屢碰壁，同事大姐都斷然拒絕，而在6月1日晚上，A男又對同事大姐糾纏，同事大姐還是拒絕，雙方爭吵起來，A男一怒之下就說，要讓女方「看看我的真面目」。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，隔日清早約6點40分，同事大姐到兼職的地點進行清潔工作時，A男竟拿著1包塑膠袋裝的、自己的大便，由後方出其不意抱住同事大姐，1手環抱大姐，1手將大便抹在大姐的嘴巴上。<br />\n<br />\n這位同事大姐被突然襲擊，她雖奮力掙扎逃脫，但身上與臉上都沾滿了A男的糞便，而A男則是逃之夭夭。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，A男今天被法院判囚7天，理由是犯了「對受害人使用刑事暴力」罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b68211a87be8f8bf1895ece279b2f0ed57ab6a","tid":976482,"uid":177734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4a5fcc4c4e18547a0b71b5f940e107215877bd","tid":976482,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"5系台灣😂😂😂"},{"pid":"364672141aa36a1fb75ef7de342767719921f13c","tid":976482,"uid":62409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/DefenselessLimitedHarrierhawk-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FDefenselessLimitedHarrierhawk-size_restricted.gif&h=20d4badc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19dfe4d43a1de5cc07753e99cbd000a6d8fad9d9","tid":976482,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"睇得太多夜勤病棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/